text: Hugo Lundevall (7 December 1892 - 16 January 1949) was a Swedish swimmer. He competed in the men's 100 metre backstroke event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1892 births Category:1949 deaths Category:Swedish male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Sweden Category:Swimmers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm Category:Male backstroke swimmers
